</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;/<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">form</span>&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><h5 id="内联表单">内联表单</h5>
<p>在<code>&lt;form&gt;</code>元素中使用类<code>.form-inline</code>。</p>
<p>类<code>.sr-only</code>可以隐藏标签。</p>
<h5 id="表单控件复选框checkbox和单选框按钮radio">表单控件（复选框checkbox和单选框按钮radio）</h5>
<ol>
<li>不管是checkbox还是radio都用label包起来了</li>
<li>checkbox连同label标签都放置在一个名为<code>.checkbox</code>的容器内</li>
<li>radio连同label标签都放置在一个名为<code>.radio</code>的容器内</li>
</ol>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">form</span> <span style="color:#658b00">role</span>=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;form&#34;</span> <span style="color:#658b00">class</span>=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;form&#34;</span>&gt;
